OL,3,CAt least 21 people killed in New Delhi
OL,4,Cbuilding fire
OL,6,FA fire swept through a New Delhi
OL,7,Fbuilding on Wednesday, killing at
OL,8,Fleast 21 people and injuring several
OL,9,Fothers, according to police.
OL,11,FThe building in the Malviya Nagar
OL,12,Fneighbourhood in the southern part of
OL,13,Fthe capital had a restaurant on the
OL,14,Fground floor and a hotel above.
OL,16,FThe predominantly residential area is
OL,17,Fdensely populated and is popular with
OL,18,Fstudents and young professionals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
