OL,3,CAt least 21 people killed in New Delhi
OL,4,Cbuilding fire
OL,6,FThe flames were extinguished with the
OL,7,Fhelp of eight fire engines, and more
OL,8,Fthan 40 people were rescued and taken
OL,9,Fto nearby hospitals, Delhi police said
OL,10,Fin a statement.
OL,12,FThe cause of the fire was not
OL,13,Fimmediately known.
OL,15,FImages from the scene showed
OL,16,Ffirefighters trying to douse the blaze
OL,17,Fas thick smoke billowed from the
OL,18,Fbuilding. Some people trapped inside
OL,19,Fwere seen hanging from windows and
OL,20,Fshouting for help as flames and smoke
OL,21,Fswept through parts of the building.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
