OL,3,CAt least 21 people killed in New Delhi
OL,4,Cbuilding fire
OL,6,FLocals also joined rescue efforts,
OL,7,Fhelping evacuate people trapped inside
OL,8,Fand carrying some of the injured to
OL,9,Fsafety.
OL,11,FSome of the victims were foreign
OL,12,Fnationals who had travelled to India
OL,13,Ffor medical treatment, local media
OL,14,Freported. Many foreign patients travel
OL,15,Fto New Delhi for medical treatment and
OL,16,Foften stay in nearby hotels or
OL,17,Fresidential accommodations during
OL,18,Ftheir visits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
