OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780538605
OL,3,CAt least 21 people killed in New Delhi
OL,4,Cbuilding fire
OL,6,FPrime Minister Narendra Modi expressed
OL,7,Fhis condolences over the deaths, his
OL,8,Foffice said in a post on X.
OL,10,FIt also said that the families of
OL,11,Fthose killed would receive 200,000
OL,12,Frupees ($2,088) each in financial
OL,13,Fassistance.
OL,15,FFires are common in India, where
OL,16,Fbuilding laws and safety norms are
OL,17,Foften flouted by builders and
OL,18,Fresidents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
